{"tid":1752234,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(行動）做國際文宣宣布民主派公投大勝，應2020雙普選","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:49:51.000Z","uid":72431,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"972b39f3273f4fa20daf8e6ae334f796edb74500","tid":1752234,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"區選唔單止係一場選舉<br />\n更重要的係一場公投<br />\n比人去投勇武革命vs和平歸中<br />\n<br />\n今次公投大勝，證明民意無逆轉，市民無同勇武切割<br />\n<br />\n港府應下台問責，2020即雙普選<br />\n<br />\n巴打們要做國際文宣宣傳民主派公投大勝<br />\n等國際幫我地都有根據d,大條道理制裁中共,Trump簽法案它快手d<br />\n<br />\n#twitter"},{"pid":"5f101f01941a4867cbb073f6fe9066191a2b4865","tid":1752234,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b79a50fa6a1c31d9ef7eccde28ee3e9b36efa0c","tid":1752234,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"請大家入一入，贏咗都要監察返政黨同議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劉青空降撞區累死後生女，民主黨唔解釋當支共處理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eAsbcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eAsbcS</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母民主黨，唔好落沙田帝怡選區𠝹票<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afvccLU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afvccLU</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨同我入一入嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eAuAHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eAuAHS</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨總部email：dphk@dphk.org<br />\n民主黨新東支部： dphknte@dphk.org<br />\n民主動力：powerfordemocracy@gmail.com<br />\n劉青（搵唔到email），但大家可以打電話問問題：36110266/84815481<br />\n<br />\n係48小時內我要聽到合理解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12e1a8bcdb135b85cf03c4ee15441b4515ff412","tid":1752234,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi